IO-AIO-Temp version 0.01
========================

Create tempfiles asynchronously.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  Guard
  IO::AIO
  File::Spec

